# Vendored port sources.
#
# The build scripts under tools/ports/ download an upstream tarball here (if
# absent) and extract it in place, then patch the tree. To make a fresh clone
# build offline / deterministically, we commit the *tarballs* but not the large
# extracted source trees (315 MB extracted vs ~31 MB of tarballs).
#
# Ignore everything (including the extracted directories like dillo-3.2.0/) ...
*
# ... but keep this .gitignore and the upstream tarballs.
!.gitignore
!*.tar.gz
!*.tar.xz
!*.tgz
!*.tar.bz2
